unsw.dungeon

Class Enemy

  • java.lang.Object
    • unsw.dungeon.Entity
      • unsw.dungeon.Enemy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer, Subject

    public class Enemy
extends Entity
implements Subject, Observer
    An enemy in the dungeon that wanders around or chases the player if it finds him. The enemy runs away from the player when the player is invincible.
    Author:
    luke Yong
